**What would change it (falsification criteria):**
- <criterion 1>
- <criterion 2>

| Date       | Engagement / Source        | Direction      | Notes |
|------------|----------------------------|----------------|-------|
| YYYY-MM-DD | <engagement / call / etc.> | SUPPORTS / CONTRADICTS / NEUTRAL | <1-2 sentences> |
```

